tournament.name: KQ 3666 The Numbered of the Beast
tournament.description:
**Cue Thriller, Vincent Price voice *clears throat***
Darkness spreads throughout the screen,
The joystick's grip, a thrilling dream.
Gamers strive to earn their fame,
In the arcade, they stake their claim.
And those who aim to seize the crown,
With strategy, they'll bring foes down,
In pixel battles fierce and swell,
They'll claim victory, as the scoreboards tell.
With treats and tricks and lots of sticks,
Welcome to KQ3666.

> Darkness spreads throughout the screen, 

> The joystick's grip, a thrilling dream. 

> Gamers strive to earn their fame, 

> In the arcade, they stake their claim. 

> And those who aim to seize the crown, 

> With strategy, they'll bring foes down, 

> In pixel battles fierce and swell, 

> They'll claim victory, as the scoreboards tell. 

> With treats and tricks and lots of sticks, 

> *Welcome to KQ3666*


### Two Day Event. The tournament will be held on Saturday starting at 2pm. Sunday will be a casual BUBG mixer and free play.


### 12 Team soft cap is in place. The schedule is subject to change.


### *Registration is $10 and can be venmo'd or paid cash the day of.*
